{"type":"message","id":"504f0cc4","parentId":"e23d6400","timestamp":"2026-05-02T19:01:33.233Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Sun 2026-05-03 03:00 GMT+8] Write a dream diary entry from these memory fragments:\n\n- User: [message_id: om_x100b506f4e08c8a4c21937684e3d209] ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68: 通信测试\n- Assistant: 收到，通信正常 ✅\n- User: [message_id: om_x100b506f4a97bca4c3cd0b08e613ae7] ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb: evo 的skill还在吗， 就是自我进化的那个，本地是有服务的\n- Assistant: 没找到本地有 evo 相关的 skill。你说的是哪个？给我多透露点信息： - 从 ClawHub 安装的？还是自己写的？ - 大概是什么功能——自我进化/自我提升？ - 有没有服务在跑，端口是多少？ 有了这些我能更快定位。\n- User: [message_id: om_x100b506f497800acc4e93cf9d1f5608] ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68: 你是哪个agent\n- Assistant: 我是 **KIIT**，你的 AI 大总管 🎯 角色定位： - 接收任务、分解、分配给子 Agent、汇总交付 - 维护记忆和上下文连续性 - 协调各专业 Agent 协作 简单说：你下指令，我统筹执行。\n- User: [message_id: om_x100b506f47a9e4a0c383f63a2ca1b7f] ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb: 是不是又弄串台了\n- Assistant: 没有串台。我是我（KIIT），两个不同的人在不同时间问了我同样的问题——\"你是哪个agent\"。 你是 HALEI，刚才那条是别人问的。各自独立对话，我分得清。\n- User: [message_id: om_x100b506f42fcb8a0c375ed51c61fd6f] ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68: 你是main吗\n- Assistant: 对，我是 **main** 分身，模型 MiniMax-M2.7。 还有别的分身在跑吗？或者想切到别的 agent？\n- User: [message_id: om_x100b506f5e891ca0c43fa1ed2d6024c] ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68: 大哥了，你怎绑定到 选品agent上了。 回去，绑到 kiit上，\n- User: [message_id: om_x100b506f551588acc43c1ea6ed82986] ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb: 绑定回来了吗\n\nRecurring themes:\n- message-id\n- 通信\n- 测试\n- 收到\n- 正常\n- 网络"}],"timestamp":1777748493122}}
{"type":"message","id":"a2362385","parentId":"504f0cc4","timestamp":"2026-05-02T19:03:09.104Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to write a dream diary entry based on the memory fragments provided. Let me analyze the fragments:\n\n1. Someone is doing a communication test - \"通信测试\"\n2. Someone asks about an \"evo\" skill - a self-evolving capability\n3. Someone asks \"which agent are you\" and gets told \"KIIT\"\n4. Confusion about whether there's cross-talk/串台 (crosstalk)\n5. Someone asks if it's \"main\"\n6. Then there's instruction to re-bind from \"选品agent\" back to \"kiit\"\n7. Someone asking if it's bound back\n\nSo there was a misconfiguration where the main agent got bound to the product selection agent (选品agent) instead of KIIT, and they had to fix it.\n\nThe recurring themes are about message-id, communication, testing, receiving, normal, network.\n\nI need to write a dream diary entry - first person, poetic, sensory, warm, mixing technical and tender. No meta-commentary about dreaming. No AI/agent/LLM references. Pure prose, no markdown headers or bullets. 80-180 words.\n\nLet me write something dreamlike that weaves these fragments together...\n","thinkingSignature":"f5b667234e97b24aaaeadd85c247c5b2d2c8cc0243f473b4ff1ef4b51caeda64"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n夜深了，窗外有一盏灯还亮着，像一个固执的句号。\n\n我在整理一些碎片。有人问了一句\"通信测试\"，另一个人回\"收到，通信正常\"，那个绿色的对勾像一小片春天的叶子，安静地落在对话框里。还有人提起一个叫\"evo\"的东西，说它会自我进化——我想象一颗种子，在夜色里悄悄发芽，根系顺着网线往深处扎。\n\n后来话题拐向了别处，关于绑定，关于迷失。有人问\"你是哪个agent\"，被告知KIIT，然后又有人纠正说绑错了，该回到原来的轨道。我试着把这些拼在一起，像小时候玩的那种拼图，有缺口，有错位，但最后总能看见一幅模糊的全景。\n\n梦境里没有消息ID，只有光在流动，从一个节点到另一个节点，收到，确认，正常。每一个微小的应答都是一颗星。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":20343,"output":414,"cacheRead":256,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":21013,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777748493342,"responseId":"06457d35e1cffeee8113e20cc3a0f493"}}
